{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"d4d4ecce94","title":"江西省宗教界人士学习班学员鸣放出的十五点反动言论","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"a6cc4f9e17","index":0,"year":1957,"month":11,"day":16,"articleId":"d4d4ecce94"}],"tags":[{"id":"56fc802eb7","name":"人民内部矛盾","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"33fa2dacb3","type":"title","text":"江西省宗教界人士学习班学员鸣放出的十五点反动言论","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d4d4ecce94"},{"id":"14cfc994b8","type":"paragraph","text":"新华社南昌16日讯  由江西省人委办公厅举办的江西省宗教界人士学习班已在10月21日正式开始学习，预计两个月结束。参加学习的有来自全省各重点市县的天主教、基督教神职人员和部分教徒一百零九人。学习期间准备分四个阶段：第一阶段是安定情绪，学习文件；第二阶段是鸣放；第三阶段是批判、辩论；最后阶段是总结。","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d4d4ecce94"},{"id":"33b9056183","type":"paragraph","text":"现在已由鸣放转到批判、辩论阶段。神职人员和教徒在鸣放中“放”出的反动言论大致可分为十五点：","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d4d4ecce94"},{"id":"050285a3d9","type":"paragraph","text":"1.\t社会主义是铁幕，没有民主自由，给人民带来灾难和痛苦。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d4d4ecce94"},{"id":"ed68d08a8f","type":"paragraph","text":"2.\t爱国会是傀儡组织，是共产党插在宗教内的一把刀子。","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d4d4ecce94"},{"id":"c96ac5c07f","type":"paragraph","text":"3.\t爱国会是叛教、裂教，是脱离教皇的组织。","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d4d4ecce94"},{"id":"51f4772b8d","type":"paragraph","text":"4.\t教会里没有帝国主义分子和反革命分子，肃反运动把人民内部矛盾扩大为敌我矛盾。","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d4d4ecce94"},{"id":"4d78ee68b5","type":"paragraph","text":"5.\t无神论与有神论者水火不相容，宗教与社会主义无法共存。","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d4d4ecce94"},{"id":"786074d229","type":"paragraph","text":"6.\t不能拥护共产党和社会主义，如拥护了就是承认唯物主义，承认它就是反对自己。","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d4d4ecce94"},{"id":"c7410e5528","type":"paragraph","text":"7.\t宁可失天下，不可失灵魂。","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d4d4ecce94"},{"id":"5c6a535bb5","type":"paragraph","text":"8.\t圣母军不是反动的，是共产党在报上渲染的。","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d4d4ecce94"},{"id":"dcc55dd85b","type":"paragraph","text":"9.\t公教与非公教的人不能在一起辩论。","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d4d4ecce94"},{"id":"a813d943f8","type":"paragraph","text":"10.\t梵蒂冈不是帝国主义，因为它不是独立国，要坚决跟它走，不要与它割断政治、经济联系。","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d4d4ecce94"},{"id":"d75b2cbfe7","type":"paragraph","text":"11.\t承认中国有两个政府：北京政府和台湾政府。","index":13,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d4d4ecce94"},{"id":"bdb34dc568","type":"paragraph","text":"12.\t爱国不分新中国与旧中国。","index":14,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d4d4ecce94"},{"id":"e52639fadd","type":"paragraph","text":"13.\t半个社会主义论：承认社会主义建设，不承认共产党领导宗教。","index":15,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d4d4ecce94"},{"id":"8d2b2614e0","type":"paragraph","text":"14.\t爱国会的进步领导是封建把头，是政府的狗腿子。","index":16,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d4d4ecce94"},{"id":"7286fb1a81","type":"paragraph","text":"15.\t宗教通论是给中国教友的警惕。（董瑛）","index":17,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d4d4ecce94"},{"id":"a8a1d989c0","type":"paragraph","text":"新华通讯社编：《内部参考》，第2363期，1957年11月20日。","index":18,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d4d4ecce94"}],"page":{"id":"f45c65bf61","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d4d4ecce94","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}